Class_03

Verbo modal

Can | can't

i can speak english

i can play 
she can speak

pronun + can

cannot - negative

can't

i can't speak english

interrogative
can he?

can + pronoun
- inverse

I can't drive becausa i'm 15 years old

can i go out today?

-------------------------------------------
o to não é essencial para verbo?

to play - brincar
to speak - falar


